{
  "stem": "3658.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we also had big, big areas of land behind our house, farms-- not farms, but land, growing things, which people were working, you know, on the land.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember that very clearly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I even had a horse there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I should have.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Good life, a good life it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Yom Tov, of course, on the holidays, everybody-- as I said, it revolved around the holidays, whether it was Sukkot or Pesach or Purim.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, I remember Purim was a very interesting holiday because the non-Jewish teachers used to also dress up as, you know, in Purim things and come to our house.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a very beautiful life, as far as, you know, the family life was concerned.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But of course, it didn't last very long that I can remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It changed, and as I said, when they came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I want to tell you one incident which I-- which is very, very much in my mind, and which I remember very clearly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When the Hungarians and the Germans came in, all of a sudden the Jewish children were separated from the non-Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Up till then, we were all going together to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this particular teacher, she was a-- she joined the party, obviously, but not her husband.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when we-- from then on, all the kids, that means whether they were 5 years, 6 years, or 15 or 16, we were all together in school.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was very-- I would say, very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she used to take-- pick on the smaller ones and hit them, and just for the sake of hitting them, and calling the different names.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember sitting back-- can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
